    "description": "Tanishq Global Group invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Assistant Store Manager at our Gurgaon location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Tanishq Global Group:\nTanishq Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Tanishq Global Group!",
